						<content leos:origin="ec"
							xml:id="imp_art_d378e819_euPe4m_Gc1xuz">
							<p leos:origin="ec" xml:id="imp_art_d378e819_euPe4m_2pdgYz">In
								order to assess the extent to which compliance with the
								accessibility requirements set out in Article 4 imposes a
								disproportionate burden, Member States shall ensure that the
								public sector body concerned takes account of relevant
								circumstances, including the following:</p>
