							<p leos:origin="ec" xml:id="moved_imp_art_d378e819_euPe4m_2pdgYz">In order to assess
								the extent to which compliance with the accessibility
								requirements set out in Article 4 imposes a disproportionate
								burden, Member States shall ensure that the public sector body
								concerned takes account of relevant circumstances, including the
								following:</p>
						</content>
					</subparagraph>
					<list leos:softmove_label="MOVED to Article 1(1a)"
						leos:origin="ec" xml:id="moved_imp_art_d378e819_euPe4m_t4Gsgl"
